Terra Firma Begins New Fund Conversations, Telegraph Reports

-- B y   H o w a r d   M u s t o e
-- 
2011-07-03T07:16:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-03/terra-firma-begins-new-fund-conversations-telegraph-reports.html
Terra Firma Capital Partners Ltd. has
spoken with at least two potential investors about the company’s
next fund, which aims to raise as much as 2.5 billion pounds ($4
billion), the Sunday Telegraph reported.  Formal marketing of Terra Firma Capital Partners IV won’t
begin until next year, the newspaper reported, citing
unidentified people close to the situation. The company will
seek investors from Asia and the  Middle East , as well as Europe
and north America, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Howard Mustoe in  London  at 
 hmustoe@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Edward Evans at   eevans3@bloomberg.net  